{"tid":1305142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[成版都係屌失焦] 運動冇大台，有具體行動提議請直接提出","createTime":"2019-07-10T19:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T00:31:55.000Z","uid":274475,"like":133,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"baf47025bf9c673dcd2ede8c5a98fc983157888b","tid":1305142,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:29:05.000Z","msg":"成版都係失焦呀，就輸喇，勿忘初心呀，十個post㩒入去十個都淨係識<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">虛化地講</span></strong>講記得五大訴求，deadline升級理論，一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">具體行動建議</span></strong>都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>運動冇大台，人人都可以吹雞做野</strong>。覺得宜家做緊嘢嘅只係支線，打唔中核心嘅話，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請具體提倡一個你認為好嘅行動出黎，並且自己先開始去做</span></strong>，work嘅自然有人有齊做。 而唔係坐響冷氣房，一味話人呢樣支線果樣失焦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcaac8fc6de0e47c031c1929244329c164642f21","tid":1305142,"uid":263161,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:34:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3d50f9f62e9d7f4bcddea20732055c77feca64c","tid":1305142,"uid":274475,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:37:11.000Z","msg":"上面個reply雖然洗版好煩，但至少啲post真係個個都有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">行動提倡</span></strong>，而唔係虛化講&quot;唔好忘記五大訴求呀&quot;<br />\n<br />\n係咁ban人行動，自己又唔提議其他行動，冇行動就真係冇人會記得五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19a27ec590ca80f05523294ac1c62fff81f11df","tid":1305142,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:38:48.000Z","msg":"最新白宮聯署！要求美國國會立即通過《香港人權民主法案》<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=24cac1f7\" data-auto-link target=